I love you.

305
00:19:21,333 --> 00:19:24,708
<i>- [singing in Japanese]</i>

306
00:19:24,791 --> 00:19:29,000
- Sorry that I never ate
all those canelés

307
00:19:29,083 --> 00:19:31,916
