308
00:19:32,000 --> 00:19:34,916
I was such a brat to you.

309
00:19:35,000 --> 00:19:38,333
I'm sorry for everything.

310
00:19:38,416 --> 00:19:41,333
<i>- [singing in Japanese]</i>

311
00:19:41,416 --> 00:19:43,125
- Thank you.

312
00:19:43,208 --> 00:19:45,166
<i>- [singing in Japanese]</i>

313
00:19:45,250 --> 00:19:49,500
<i>♪ ♪</i>

314
00:19:49,583 --> 00:19:52,750
- I can't believe
you wrote that.

315
00:19:52,833 --> 00:19:56,000
I should thank you
for all of it.

316
00:19:56,083 --> 00:20:00,125
<i>- P.S., I'm giving you one</i>
<i>of my favorite pictures.</i>

317
00:20:01,125 --> 00:20:03,666
<i>You don't have to keep it,</i>
<i>but I hope you do.</i>

318
00:20:06,041 --> 00:20:08,000
- Hey.
- [grunts]

319
00:20:08,083 --> 00:20:10,791
