324
00:20:18,458 --> 00:20:20,500
What's the big idea?

325
00:20:20,583 --> 00:20:22,041
[grunts]

326
00:20:22,125 --> 00:20:23,833
- You had better not think
you're gonna be alone now

327
00:20:23,916 --> 00:20:25,125
or something!

328
00:20:25,208 --> 00:20:27,083
I'm sticking by your side
forever and ever,

329
00:20:27,166 --> 00:20:28,791
like I was covered
in super glue,

330
00:20:28,875 --> 00:20:30,083
